    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276250/extras/0cfce325106b11ac4f5031507a0aa62f.avif?t=1764557948\" width=800 height=223 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Mato Fragments》讲述Neo City的起源，这是一座爵士时代风格的绿洲城市，存在于反乌托邦与废墟之间。城市中融合了多元文化、时间线与技术。然而，随着一场颠覆城市的阴谋浮现，Neo City的脆弱和平岌岌可危。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276250/extras/0d5f087a6a3c2228972e11d00015e3ca.avif?t=1764557948\" width=800 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是城市中最擅长社交与情报搜集的人物，可进入“侦探模式”仔细观察角色，从而推断出他们的真实意图。巧妙地交易情报，将会影响角色行为与选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276250/extras/14fbead8849f0fe1f0fa34603cb30a5e.avif?t=1764557948\" width=800 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你与这座城市被困在一个五天的时间循环中。每个决定都至关重要，一次错误的选择就可能让你重新回到时间循环的起点。研究形形色色的角色，搜集信息，帮助他们避免走向灾难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276250/extras/ad749942b4995e72180605cc8594fad4.avif?t=1764557948\" width=800 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 《Mato Fragments》以独特且风格化的美术呈现，将玩家带入一个融合传统与现代亚洲元素的黑暗复古未来主义世界。无论是艺术风格、建筑，还是角色设计，都充满亚洲特色。</p>",
